General.Name: Hamster Marketplace Token
General.Description: The Hamster Marketplace will allow vendors to get access to markets that they cannot afford now and will provide access to the audience of early adopters and technology fans. The HMT token is an ERC20 compliant token and is to be used within their marketplace.

ICO.Description:
The Hamster Marketplace will allow vendors to get access to markets that they cannot afford now and will provide access to the audience of early adopters and technology fans

The HMT token is an ERC20 compliant token and is to be used within their marketplace.

Team:

  • Denis Bulavin CEO ;
  • Yegor Kotkin COO ;
  • Chris Lovell Community outreach partner 
  • John Pawin Project manager

The Hamster Marketplace will be holding its ICO on February 19th. 2018. The ICO token supply represents 51% of the total token supply, so there will be a total of 7,000,000 tokens available, for 2$ USD  each during the offering. The ICO funding target is 2,000,000$ USD, the funding cap is 14,000,000$ USD and is expected to end on March 19th 2018 or when the funding cap is reached. Any unsold/remaining tokens will destroyed.

The token will not be mineable.

The HMT ICO features bounty campaign.
